<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>The heavenly State ƲIT163</title>
<time_sig>L.M. (8.8.8.8.)</time_sig>
<aka>Chihowa im ʋlla yʋto</aka>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Chihowa im ʋlla yʋto
 Chitolit taloho̱wa cha,
 In Chitokaka yatukma
 Aiokpahancha hi oke.

[V2]
 Chukfʋlhpobushi yʋmmak osh
 Chumpʋt pi okchalinchi tok,
 Yʋmmak o̱ im ʋlla pia,
 Achit na̱ yukpa hi oke.

[V3]
 Yohmikma okla chinto kʋt
 Aholhtina mʋt iksho hosh
 Chihowa itikba yoka
 Aiasha na billia he.

[V4]
 Yohmikma homak pilla ma
 Abeka, illi, nukha̱klo,
 Nishkin okchi aiena kʋt
 A takala he keyushke.</lyrics>
<author>George L. Williams</author>
<hymn_number>163</hymn_number>
</song>